description:
Gene Wolfe - The Claw of the Conciliator (The Book of the New Sun #2) 



In the darkling depths of the fantastical future, the torturer Severian continues his journey of exile to the city Thrax. He carries with him the ancient executioner's sword, Terminus Est, and the Claw of the Conciliator, a gem of extraterrestrial power and beauty which no man is meant to possess. In a world of magical beauty and awesome terrors, Severian travels the perilous road towards his destiny.




Narrated by: Jonathan Davis
